  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BOp, IPropertySet, Serializable, Cloneable

    public final class InsertStatementsOp
extends AbstractAddRemoveStatementsOp
    Vectored insert operator for RDF Statements. The solutions flowing through this operator MUST bind the s, p, o, and (depending on the database mode) MAY bind the c variable. Those variables correspond to the Subject, Predicate, Object, and Context/Graph position of an RDF Statement respectively. On input, the variables must be real IVs. The IVCache does NOT need to be set. The output is an empty solution.
